                        "Add oil",
                        "Add vanilla extract",
                        "Mix until glossy and fully combined"
                    ],
                    "timer_minutes": 0
                },
                {
                    "step": 4,
                    "title": "Mix Dry Ingredients",
                    "actions": [
                        "Whisk flour, pumpkin pie spice, cinnamon, salt, baking soda, and baking powder in a separate bowl",
                        "Whisk well to evenly distribute spices and leavening"
                    ],
                    "timer_minutes": 0
                },
                {
                    "step": 5,
                    "title": "Combine Wet and Dry",
                    "actions": [
                        "Add half of the dry mixture to the wet ingredients",
                        "Mix until just combined",
                        "Add remaining dry ingredients",
                        "Mix gently until no dry flour remains",
                        "Do not overmix"
                    ],
                    "timer_minutes": 0
                },
                {
                    "step": 6,
                    "title": "Add Chocolate Chips",
                    "actions": [
                        "Add chocolate chips",
                        "Fold gently with a spatula until evenly distributed"
                    ],
                    "timer_minutes": 0
                },
                {
                    "step": 7,
                    "title": "Scoop and Bake",
                    "actions": [
                        "Scoop dough onto baking sheets, spacing cookies 2 inches apart",
                        "Bake at 375°F for 15 minutes",
                        "Cookies are done when edges are set and tops look matte"
                    ],
                    "timer_minutes": 15
                },
                {
                    "step": 8,
                    "title": "Cool",
                    "actions": [
